headline: WEC Energy Group reports second-quarter results
summary: WEC Energy Group (NYSE: WEC) today reported net income of $245.4 million, or 76 cents per share, for the second quarter of 2025 — up from $211.3 million, or 67 cents per share, in last year's second quarter.
